<a name="sliceadmin"></a>
<h4>2. Web Site Manager and Slice Administrator</h4>
(Documents for people configuring the ActionApps using the web-based interface)
<ul>
  <li>Manual (get your own copy in the <a href="https://www.apc.org/actionapps/english/manual/download.html" target="_blank">downloads</a>
    section of the ActionApps website)
    <ul>
      <li>Chapter III - Webmaster's Guide<BR>
        <i>Description:</i> This section guides you through setting up a Action
        App 'slice' for your web site and other typical administration tasks.
        Here you will find step-by-step instructions for how to perform these
        tasks. One of the primary tasks of the slice administrator is to configure
        how your slice appears on your organization's Web site, and how ActionApps
        appear to staff members and volunteers. </li>
    </ul>
  <li><a href="http://apc-aa.sourceforge.net/faq/#Slice">FAQ for Slice Administrators</a><BR>
