    <em>Description:</em> Explains the ideas and work flow for reader management
    and the related features.
  <li><a href="anonym.html">Anonymous forms for posting and editing</a> <br>
    <em>Description:</em> Everything you need to create and use anonymous forms.
 <li><a href="http://apc-aa.sourceforge.net/slices/index.shtml">Tutorial example of slice module</a> <br>
    <em>Description:</em> Demonstrates all the main features of site module. You
can see also to site administration (in AA), there the site code is
strongly commented
  <li><a href="http://apc-aa.sourceforge.net/apc-aa/admin/index.php3">Tutorial on using AA input fields</a> <br>
